{"tid":1871813,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中銀銀行七宗罪","createTime":"2020-02-09T16:52:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-08T17:24:39.000Z","uid":348807,"like":4,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"044a484ac54a02766d2c4717a0c66dc72da60075","tid":1871813,"uid":348807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T16:52:41.000Z","msg":"繼恒生銀行七宗罪<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1852853/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1852853/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n借朋友ac出post<br />\n除左關口、醫護、飲食呢啲超高危行業外，其實銀行都係接觸勁撚多鄰國人嘅中高危行業<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但中銀偏偏就好撚多戇鳩嘢攞員工性命黎較飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.疫症高峰時期，分行主管區主管死捽難捽，要瘋狂約客，不理前線生死。<br />\n2.假home office，公司表明會安排同事home office，實際只有back office 同事翻一日，home office一日。前線理得你死，一星期翻足6日，最多放你一日。原來back office同事接觸客戶風險仲俾前線仲高？<br />\n3.口罩派發都係沒生產地，沒任何防護功能，都係內地黑心口罩。而且有分行口罩限量派發，什至有員工沒有口罩。<br />\n4.免費叫外賣午飯叫去到2月15日，之後就自己出去食飯，感染左就翻黎分行/內部播毒。<br />\n5.每間分行開門/關門都沒有預留時間清潔，只有營業時間有一位清潔人員，什至有分行沒清潔人員。5點銀行關門，清潔工人5點下班，客户5點後還在分行，等如5點後沒有人清潔。<br />\n6.中銀冇開門嘅分行有部份人係完全唔使返工，佢哋名為叫clean team，係等有分行有人返唔到工或者成間分行開唔到門，佢哋就會喺其他無開既分行上班，但係呢班人淨係係屋企坐。呢個時間佢地淨係做stand by，超唔公平，佢地仲有糧出架，要開門既分行繼續開，開門既分行同事繼續死做。<br />\n7.員工家屬曾經回到國內不需隔離，只需申報就可以，完全莫視會被感染和回公司傳播病菌的風險。<br />\n<br />\n總結：中銀，不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e61bd9f4b8626b8224fe1b88e0cc4b484367f088","tid":1871813,"uid":27349,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T16:55:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"61673096dc5dff9a2009d56990b3dcc8ad9e084c","tid":1871813,"uid":276415,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T16:57:40.000Z","msg":"無人想知係BO蚑堆死剷有咩待遇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7f3970da65762554d928bbea83813e98682f53d","tid":1871813,"uid":104034,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T01:12:14.000Z","msg":"今日開始再無每天$500津貼啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 叫人home office但又無notebook, 迫人返工"},{"pid":"c49da41b25299c966699e362cbacca2df1257ae2","tid":1871813,"uid":3302,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T01:14:08.000Z","msg":"做中資 冇良知"},{"pid":"a1b305fb318502cf8e95f45cb687a91fdecd9552","tid":1871813,"uid":104034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T03:50:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63ca1d73bf24f59c4de3187cb967b70c59f438cd","tid":1871813,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T04:00:36.000Z","msg":"唔認同你第2點講法。<br />\n因父母生意問題，迫住要係hsbc/ 中銀開戶口。<br />\n但原來hsbc要戶口要朝早9點排隊先開到，所以最後迫住係中銀開戶口。<br />\n<br />\n咁前線留晒係屋企home office , 搵咩人幫客開戶口？"},{"pid":"5df84562a50910b22aed97eea98429f40996424d","tid":1871813,"uid":104034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T15:41:40.000Z","msg":"分行同事有1500津貼"},{"pid":"3b830400c348f1d94428f0ae0589abf87fc68f3f","tid":1871813,"uid":104034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5df84562a50910b22aed97eea98429f40996424d","tid":1871813,"uid":104034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T15:41:40.000Z","msg":"分行同事有1500津貼"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T11:34:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04fad9351a6037ac5e543cec33c745815921101d","tid":1871813,"uid":115191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T15:28:39.000Z","msg":"依家日日收工仲要留係分行cold call 約客見<br />\n依家啲客都唔敢落街啦 見乜9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=